    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Objects, food, or other materials that are considered sacrifices or oblations, presented to a god, saint, sacred place, etc., as an act of worship, devotion, or homage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
