      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlamantli, tlacualli zo ceyoc tlamantli tlen momachtilia pan ce campeca ica ce totiozin, zantoh, canahya malhuilli, quence ce tlamantli tlen motlepanitta zo tlen quichihuilia ce campeca.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
